Fixed some ad leftovers and anti-adblock ads, but I'm not sure if this anti-adblock popup should be fixed in this case.

Adding those rules:
```adblock
echo-online.de#@#.adsbygoogle
echo-online.de#$#.adBlockerLayer { display: none !important; }
echo-online.de#$#html.fixedBackground > body { overflow: auto !important; }
echo-online.de#$#html.fixedBackground { position: static !important; }
$script,redirect-rule=noopjs,domain=echo-online.de
echo-online.de#%#//scriptlet('prevent-element-src-loading', 'script', '/echo-online\.de\/iomm\/latest/bootstrap\/loader\.js|nativendo\.de|stroeerdigitalgroup\.de/')
```
to user rules should fix it.

@BlazDT Could you please take a look?
